Package: cdeMissing
Type: Package
Title:  with Missing Covariates in Longitudinal Mixed Models
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Jiangshan", family = "Zhang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = jiszhang@ucdavis.edu")
  )
Description: Implements a CDE-style approach for longitudinal mixed models with missing covariates.
    The package augments long-format data with missingness indicators and timepoint dummies, then fits
    LMMs (via 'nlme') or GLMMs (via 'lme4') using a consistent, configurable interface.
